c: 2
v: 127
t: "N’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahim (iii) mugihe yasanura iyo nyubakwa aduza impome ziryo sengero ritagatifu ariyo (Al’ka’abat) ari kumwe n’ikibondo ciwe Ismail (iii) bose hamwe baciye basaba Imana yabo bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu n’utwemerere, mu vy’ukuri ni wewe wumva kandi ni wewe nyene ubumenyi buhagije"